data.description: Charming 3 BR/2BA one level home situated on a spacious lot in a quiet neighborhood. Location, location, location; schools, churches, dining, activities, all in close proximity. SS appliances, wood burning fireplace in great room, large screened in porch, perfect for entertaining (could be converted to carport or garage). Bonus utility/flex space. The flow of this home is amazing with large rooms throughout. Bonus expandable space in attic. This is a must see at this price!
